#: ../../../release_details/9.5/ensight-reader-improvements.md:1
msgid "EnsightCombinedReader: Performance improvements pass"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/ensight-reader-improvements.md:3
msgid ""
"Improve performances of the new vtkEnSightGoldCombinedReader in various "
"ways, especially when reading large binary files containing nfaced/"
"tetrahedron cells:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/ensight-reader-improvements.md:4
msgid ""
"The tetrahedron cell-building logic now uses a tetrahedron-specific "
"vtkUnstructredGrid::InsertNextCell call"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/ensight-reader-improvements.md:5
msgid ""
"Tetrahedron cells connectivity data are read as one block rather than cell-"
"by-cell"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/ensight-reader-improvements.md:6
msgid ""
"Add new \"skip\" methods to vtkEnSightDataSet which implement dedicated "
"logic to ignore file cell sections. The logic is duplicated a bit from the "
"equivalent reading methods at the benefit of much faster parsing during the "
"RequestInfo pass (to get the parts names)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/ensight-reader-improvements.md:7
msgid "Fix an int overflow that could occur while seeking ahead in large files"
msgstr ""
